文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: The four primary Zircaloy fuel cladding deformation phenomena—axial elongation, circumferential creep, ovalization, and ridging-have been investigated for fuel irradiated in four modern pressurized water reactors.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: The axial elongation of fueled and nonfueled rods is examined by a regression fit for dependence on fluence, clad texture, yield stress, applied stress and, for fuel rods, fuel pellet length to diameter ratio.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: For fueled rods, only fluence and stress are found to be important

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: For nonfueled rods, the texture is found to influence elongation.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: The circumferential creep strain data from nonfueled rods are also analyzed by a regression analysis to estimate the effects of time, flux, applied stress, temperature, yield stress, and texture.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: The primary difference is between recrystallized and stress-relief-annealed cladding with the degree of retained cold work having less effect.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: Ovalization of fueled and nonfueled rods is observed although analysis is difficult.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: Clad ridging develops in fueled rods, usually in a time period between one and two reactor cycles and almost always after three cycles.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk1
证据片段: However, the maximum ridge height occurs before the end of two reactor cycles.

证据片段: The average diameters of 36 B&W rods (12 rods after each of the first three reactor cycles), measured at each of the lower 18 mandrels for each rod, are summarized® in Figs. 5 through 8.

文献ID: STP754-EB-Zirconium in the Nuclear Industry_5th Volume_019_chunk5
证据片段: The complete data set is 648 B&W measurements and 60 CE measurements.

证据片段: The carbon content of the cladding was included after out-of-pile tests by CE on SSM cladding [42] agreed with Charquet et al [43] that the thermal creep rate increases as carbon decreases.

证据片段: The earliest measurements in the data set occur after approximately one year of irradiation.
